Boards:
(3x3) width = 5 chars, height = 3
_|_|_
_|_|_
 | |

(4x4) width = 7 chars, height = 4
_|_|_|_
_|_|_|_
_|_|_|_
 | | |

(5x5) width = 9 chars, height = 5
_|_|_|_|_
_|_|_|_|_
_|_|_|_|_
_|_|_|_|_
 | | | |

width = n + (n-1)
height = n

for even columns we will insert a '_'.
for odd columns we will insert a '|'

Look at magic squares
